{"tid":1780335,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"漫畫戰線諗得過？","createTime":"2019-12-12T09:35:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-12T09:58:40.000Z","uid":267877,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"595394f10ed3571be09121108b33d624605ee528","tid":1780335,"uid":267877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T09:35:24.000Z","msg":"各位相信漫畫的影響力嗎？ <br />\n<br />\n日前Batman兩位漫畫家狠狠咁屌打中共，引起迥響<br />\n<br />\n「世上某些政治實體深深畏懼著自我表達的力量，所以他們才會如此害怕一張圖片&hellip;反正他們遲早也會崩解的。」 -- Frank Miller<br />\n<br />\n「人們需要一些能夠激勵他們的事物，同時為了自己的自由而戰，這正是《黃金之子》所要傳達的思想。」 -- Rafael Gramp&aacute;<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Mt8sw2U.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMt8sw2U.jpg&h=a5c1da7f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實The Golden Child一出街已引起國際關注同報導<br />\n美國Business Insider：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.businessinsider.com/dc-comics-batman-ad-pulled-hong-kong-protest-china-2019-11\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdc-comics-batman-ad-pulled-hong-kong-protest-china-2019-11&d=Vh0AUGqI%2BhuKY3uG7C8Fc%2BDrFCZ%2FFQqiuLijmhCLlc8%3D&h=0c343974\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.businessinsider.com/dc-comics-batman-ad-pulled-hong-kong-protest-china-2019-11</a><br />\n<br />\n英國《衛報》：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.theguardian.com/books/2019/nov/29/dc-drops-batman-image-after-claims-it-supports-hong-kong-unrest\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Fbooks%2F2019%2Fnov%2F29%2Fdc-drops-batman-image-after-claims-it-supports-hong-kong-unrest&d=Vh0AUGqI%2BhuKY3uG7C8Fc%2BDrFCZ%2FFQqiuLijmhCLlc8%3D&h=752d329f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.theguardian.com/books/2019/nov/29/dc-drops-batman-image-after-claims-it-supports-hong-kong-unrest</a><br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n另一邊廂，日本動漫《我的英雄學院》MV 都疑似講香港，當時大陸又有反應<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NX0eWvb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNX0eWvb.jpg&h=f3007e63&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n//MV 出現大量疑似香港抗爭元素，包括防毒面具，甚至「民間記者會」。該作在大陸網路引起討論後即下架，而日本原版的完整片段，亦在 Youtube 被撤片，原因不明；餘下的短版 MV 則在留言欄引起大量討論。有網民批評作品「讚頌暴徒」，指它毫無價值 (Worthless)。//<br />\n---------------------------------------<br />\n既然啲畫可以引起國際反應，小妹覺得可以集合群眾力量，呼籲不同漫畫作者企係正義一方！至於呼籲邊D作者呢？小妹心儀《ONE PIECE》海賊王，點解？<br />\n<br />\n1.\t作者撐自由<br />\n有睇開既朋友就知，海賊王經常滲透革命思想，路飛同革命軍佢地成日從極權手上解放人民，由此相信尾田都支持自由民主價值<br />\n<br />\n當中一話係講極權（政府）為左奉承更高級既極權（世界政府），計劃燒死晒所謂「污點」（垃圾山既街坊），SABO好緊張之際，發現街上既貴族都明知計劃但仍然生活如常（似唔似呢排既香港？平行時空。。。。。。）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Jz0VFW5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJz0VFW5.jpg&h=8a03a432&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4ibYDJR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4ibYDJR.jpg&h=62d6640f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wbPSJa9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwbPSJa9.jpg&h=319669b9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oXFuLpz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoXFuLpz.jpg&h=c5e02e19&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pnCpzh0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpnCpzh0.jpg&h=71068310&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UT9n5pM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUT9n5pM.jpg&h=78e6a0f1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9fUCUib.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9fUCUib.jpg&h=28698568&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rn7kR4W.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Frn7kR4W.jpg&h=2831e65d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n漫畫入面既「布魯賈姆海賊團」就係極權既棋子。。。故事入面比人當condom，本身獲承諾升官發財，點知呢，其實人地一早打算完事後燒死埋佢地。。似邊個？<br />\n<br />\n＜語錄＞<br />\nSABO：「ACE！LUFFY！這個城鎮大瘋狂了！大家都知道晚一點就有人要死了，但卻還能夠吃飯！還叫小孩唸書！」"},{"pid":"8717ba119989799bf6d93d2199bf5e63417c3380","tid":1780335,"uid":267877,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T09:35:38.000Z","msg":"2.\t漫畫人氣高<br />\n日本作為漫畫大國， 我地睇睇佢2018年度漫畫銷量排名：<br />\n第1位：ONE PIECE<br />\n第2位：我的英雄學院<br />\n第3位：進擊的巨人<br />\n<br />\n日本goo ranking網站今年３月「平成Jump漫畫」票選排行：<br />\n第1位：ONE PIECE<br />\n第2位：火影忍者<br />\n第3位：龍珠Z<br />\n<br />\n睇埋ＷＩＫＩ：<br />\n《ONE PIECE》1997年起連載，之後被改編成各種載體的系列作品，至今已出版90餘冊單行本。並長佔《週刊少年Jump》人氣榜的第一名，單行本已發行30多個國家翻譯版本。至2019年3月止，目前全世界累計總發行量已經突破4億5000萬冊（日本占3億9000萬冊）。<br />\n<br />\n《ONE PIECE》影響力絕對唔惹少，所以！小妹呼籲各位花少少時間一齊去轟炸集英社（出版社）個MAIL BOX！將香港人既聲音傳送比尾田，等佢幫我地畫出黎比世界睇！<br />\n<br />\n集英社官方營運網站「 MANGA Plus by SHUEISHA 」Feedback Page：<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://mangaplus.shueisha.co.jp/feedback\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmangaplus.shueisha.co.jp%2Ffeedback&d=Vh0AUGqI%2BhuKY3uG7C8Fc%2BDrFCZ%2FFQqiuLijmhCLlc8%3D&h=2af0328e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://mangaplus.shueisha.co.jp/feedback</a><br />\n<br />\n拙劣Template如下（各位最好自由發揮）<br />\n<br />\nDear Eiichiro Oda,<br />\n<br />\nI love One Piece and I am writing to seek for your support! <br />\n<br />\nHong Kong Protesters are fighting hard against tyranny and police brutality like Luffy and Sabo in One Piece. Many young protesters were shot, raped and killed.<br />\n<br />\nWe have 5 demands : <br />\n-Full withdrawal of the extradition bill<br />\n-An independent commission of inquiry into alleged police brutality<br />\n-Retracting the classification of protesters as &ldquo;rioters&rdquo;<br />\n-Amnesty for arrested protesters<br />\n-Dual universal suffrage, meaning for both the Legislative Council and the Chief Executive <br />\n<br />\nWe need strong allies like you on our road to victory! We believe that your artwork can influence the world that propaganda is very critical for us at the moment. It would be our honour to have your comic as our strong aid!<br />\n<br />\nThank You!<br />\n<br />\nRegards,<br />\nHong Kong fan"},{"pid":"067524f70515af605c9dc322c3642be441884c5a","tid":1780335,"uid":267877,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T09:36:01.000Z","msg":"其他漫畫家、藝術家都有得諗，集思廣益，相信文宣的力量！！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n五大訴求，缺一不可！<br />\n另，今天活動：送別周同學/齊上齊落集會<br />\n------------------------------------------<br />\n參考連結：<br />\nACGER編輯部　30/11/2018　漫畫銷量2018年度排行Top10<br />\n<a href=\"https://hkacger.com/archives/72189/%E6%BC%AB%E7%95%AB%E9%8A%B7%E9%87%8F2018%E5%B9%B4%E5%BA%A6%E6%8E%92%E8%A1%8Ctop10%EF%BC%9A%E7%AC%AC3%E4%BD%8D%E9%80%B2%E6%93%8A%E7%9A%84%E5%B7%A8%E4%BA%BA%E3%80%81%E7%AC%AC2%E4%BD%8D%E6%88%91%E7%9A%84/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkacger.com%2Farchives%2F72189%2F%25E6%25BC%25AB%25E7%2595%25AB%25E9%258A%25B7%25E9%2587%258F2018%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E5%25BA%25A6%25E6%258E%2592%25E8%25A1%258Ctop10%25EF%25BC%259A%25E7%25AC%25AC3%25E4%25BD%258D%25E9%2580%25B2%25E6%2593%258A%25E7%259A%2584%25E5%25B7%25A8%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E3%2580%2581%25E7%25AC%25AC2%25E4%25BD%258D%25E6%2588%2591%25E7%259A%2584%2F&d=Vh0AUGqI%2BhuKY3uG7C8Fc%2BDrFCZ%2FFQqiuLijmhCLlc8%3D&h=7f41b439\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hkacger.com/archives/72189/%E6%BC%AB%E7%95%AB%E9%8A%B7%E9%87%8F2018%E5%B9%B4%E5%BA%A6%E6%8E%92%E8%A1%8Ctop10%EF%BC%9A%E7%AC%AC3%E4%BD%8D%E9%80%B2%E6%93%8A%E7%9A%84%E5%B7%A8%E4%BA%BA%E3%80%81%E7%AC%AC2%E4%BD%8D%E6%88%91%E7%9A%84/</a><br />\n<br />\n香港01　8/3/2019　日本網民票選平成Jump漫畫排行Top15　全是陪伴90後成長的經典<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E9%96%8B%E7%BD%90/302703/%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E7%B6%B2%E6%B0%91%E7%A5%A8%E9%81%B8%E5%B9%B3%E6%88%90jump%E6%BC%AB%E7%95%AB%E6%8E%92%E8%A1%8Ctop15-%E5%85%A8%E6%98%AF%E9%99%AA%E4%BC%B490%E5%BE%8C%E6%88%90%E9%95%B7%E7%9A%84%E7%B6%93%E5%85%B8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E9%2596%258B%25E7%25BD%2590%2F302703%2F%25E6%2597%25A5%25E6%2